high_descs: Head to the table to the left.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn around, bring the mug to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Take the chilled mug back to the coffee machine.
Put the chilled mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the table with the coffee maker.
Pick up coffee mug from the coffee maker.
Turn around and stand in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the mug in the fridge, and close the door, wait a few seconds, and take the mug out of the fridge.
Turn around and face the table with the coffee maker on it.
Place the mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To chill a mug for coffee.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the dining table
grab the white cup on the table
turn around to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, put the cup in, wait a while, take the cup out, close the refrigerator
turn around to the table
put the cup back on the table
anns.task_desc: cool the cup from the table in the refrigerator, put it back on the table

high_descs: Turn around and make a right toward the wooden table.
Pick up the coffee mug sitting in the coffee maker.
Walk to the refrigerator directly behind you.
Open the refrigerator doors and place the mug on the top shelf, close the doors for a few seconds, then open the doors again and remove the mug.
Return to the wooden kitchen table behind you.
Place the mug back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Cooling a cup of coffee from under the coffee maker in the refrigerator.
